            <!-- Description Text -->
            <TextBlock Width="700" Text="GameWorld is an exciting project that aims to create an immersive and engaging gaming experience for players. With its innovative features and cutting-edge technology, GameWorld pushes the boundaries of what is possible in the gaming industry.
